    question: "Does your window cleaning include screens and tracks?",
    answer: "Yes. Our window cleaning service includes more than just the glass. We also:\n\n• Screens: Remove and lightly wash or wipe down screens to clear away dust, pollen, and debris.\n• Tracks & Sills: Wipe and clean window tracks and sills to remove dirt buildup and ensure a neat finish.\n\nThis complete approach leaves your windows sparkling, functional, and refreshed—inside and out."
  },
  {
    question: "Do I need to be home during the window washing service?",
    answer: "No, you don’t need to be home. Many clients provide entry or access instructions (for interiors) and we handle the rest. Our technicians are trained, background-checked professionals who will respect your property and follow any special directions you provide. When we’re done, we’ll ensure everything is left secure, clean, and in order."
